{"about_the_game":"Nine Territories Legends-the Sun Disaster is a single player card game of Roguelike based on the story -ten Suns coming out together in the Overseas West Classic Chapter of the Shan Hai Classic. The game innovatively incorporates board elements into itself, bringing new fun and intellectual challenges to the card play.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/\u6807\u98981.jpg?t=1689832867\" /><br>During the reign of the Emperor Yao, a strange phenomenon appeared in the sky, ten suns coming out together, and the world suffered a severe drought. All kinds of ferocious beasts took advantage of the opportunity to come out of their nests, bringing disasters to the world where people were struggling and casualties were extremely heavy. The Sacrifice Personnel-N\u00fcchou(a person name, from the Shan Hai Classic) deduced and learned that currently the seal of the five elements must be broken before the power of the sun can be weakened. All the clans were ordered to save the world from fire and water. But the truth is revealed in the end...<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/01.gif?t=1689832867\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/\u6807\u98982.jpg?t=1689832867\" /><br>\u00b7A strategy game based on deck construction and board elimination<br>\u00b7The innovative board mode brings new fun and challenges to the card play<br>\u00b7The Roguelike card library construction contains multi-characters and multi-genres<br>\u00b7The unique block combination and revenue bonus system<br>\u00b7Free and rich explorations of random events<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/03.gif?t=1689832867\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/s